{"article_id":"QR9tYSMNi3ZLIYvy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"State media accuses Trump administration of acting like a ' bunch of hoodlums '","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"as tariffs on $ 34bn in Chinese goods go into effect","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"A long-threatened trade war between the US and China has got under way","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"after the world ' s two largest economies imposed tariffs on each other .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The US implemented tariffs on $ 34bn in Chinese goods ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to which Beijing responded with levies on a similar quantity of US imports .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Minutes after the US tariffs went into effect at 12.01am on Friday US time ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"a spokesperson for China ' s ministry of commerce said ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"\" China promised not to fire the first shot ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"but","depth":13},{"id":10,"text":"in order to safeguard the country ' s core interests as well as that of the people ,","depth":14},{"id":11,"text":"it is forced to fight back , \"","depth":14},{"id":12,"text":"according to Xinhua .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"The ministry stopped short of saying","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"China had implemented its retaliatory duties .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Later on Friday , a spokesman for the ministry of foreign affairs said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"after the US tariffs kicked in ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Chinese tariffs on US goods had immediately gone into effect .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Ahead of the tariffs , Chinese state media published a series of editorials","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"criticising the US","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and emphasising the country ' s readiness for a trade war .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Chinese companies and investors girded for the worst ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"while economists cautioned","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"any impact on the economy would be minimal .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"The Iowa farmers on the frontline of Trump 's trade war with China","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"\" If what the US wants is to escalate a trade war with China ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"then so be it .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"A little fighting may be the only way","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"the Trump administration clears its mind","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"and allows everyone to sober up , \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"the state-run Global Times said on Friday .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"\" The Trump administration is behaving like a gang of hoodlums with its shakedown of other countries , particularly China , \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"said an English-language article in the China Daily .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"On Thursday , a spokesperson for China ' s ministry of commerce said","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"the US will be \" opening fire on the whole world","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"and also opening fire on itself . \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"China ' s central banker said","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Trump ' s promised tariffs of 25 % on $ 50bn of Chinese goods","depth":15},{"id":39,"text":"- Friday ' s $ 34bn","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"to be followed by $ 16bn in a few weeks -","depth":16},{"id":41,"text":"would shave 0.2 percentage points off of China ' s GDP","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"and the \" overall impact would be limited , \"","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"according to Xinhua .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Still , Chinese investors and companies were worried .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"The Shanghai Composite index was down 1.1 % ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"after reaching more than a two-year low this week","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"before rallying","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"after the tariff deadline passed .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Chinese manufacturers have already been hit by a strengthening yuan","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that has made exports more expensive .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Q & A","depth":3},{"id":52,"text":"What is the China-US trade war about ?","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"Show Hide","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"The roots of the dispute come from US president Donald Trump ' s \" America first \" project","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"to protect the US ' position as the world ' s leading economy ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"while encouraging businesses to hire more workers in the US and to manufacture their products there .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Trump complains of a large trade deficit with China ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"which he views as a symbol of the US ' s decline as a manufacturing powerhouse .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Chinese imports to the US totalled $ 539.5bn last year ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"while $ 120.3bn was sold the other way","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"- leaving a trade deficit of $ 419.2bn .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"The president has accused Beijing of \" unfair \" trade policies ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"including allowing the theft of US companies ' intellectual property .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"The threat of import tariffs on Chinese goods is being used as leverage in talks","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"where Trump is seeking changes to Beijing ' s trade policy .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Tariffs have been imposed by Washington on some Chinese goods","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"sold in the US","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"for about a year .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"They came on top of broader tariffs","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"used by Trump","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"that have hit China and other trading partners such as the EU , Canada and Mexico ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"on goods","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"including steel and aluminium .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"In May 2019 the US president further ratcheted up existing import tariffs of 10 % on $ 200bn","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"( £153bn )","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"of Chinese goods","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"sold in the US","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"to 25 % ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"hitting everything on a long list of products .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Trump has previously warned","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that 25 % tariffs could be slapped on a further $ 325bn of goods in future","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"- which would mean all Chinese imports","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"being covered by tariffs .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Richard Partington and Jasper Jolly","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"\" One of the biggest competitive advantages of Chinese exports is their low price .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"After tariffs are imposed ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"prices for Chinese made goods will rise","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"and we ' ll lose our comparative advantage , \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"said a representative for Sanhua Micro-Channel ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"which makes components for air conditioners in China ' s eastern Zhejiang province .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"The company said","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"it had already moved some production to the US and Mexico","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"and would likely move more .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Others say","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"they are turning their focus to Chinese consumers .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"\" China is a big market for us .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"If we can seize our own market ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"we will be less affected by the trade war , \"","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"said a spokesperson for Topsun , a furniture manufacturer in Zhejiang province .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Chinese tariffs on US agricultural products will also affect Chinese importers .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Lu ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"who runs a shop at a fruit retail centre in central Beijing ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"the prices of imported US fruit","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"- subject to tariffs of as much as 50 % -","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"are certain to rise .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Still , he understands the US perspective .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"\" Americans want to earn more money","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"so they started a trade war .","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"I can understand that .","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"Who doesn ' t want to earn more money ? \"","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"Chinese media reported","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"a container ship","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"carrying 70,000 tons of US soybeans","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"was racing to reach the port of Dalian on Friday","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"before retaliatory tariffs were implemented .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Some Chinese ports have stopped clearing US goods","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"while waiting for official guidance ,","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"according to Reuters .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"Trump has threatened to raise tariffs","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"if China retaliates to roughly the value of total Chinese exports to the US last year of $ 506bn .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"He told reporters aboard Air Force One on Thursday ,","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"\" You have another 16","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"( billion dollars )","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"in two weeks ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"and then ,","depth":17},{"id":128,"text":"as you know ,","depth":18},{"id":129,"text":"we have $ 200bn in abeyance","depth":18},{"id":130,"text":"and then after the $ 200bn , we have $ 300bn in abeyance .","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"Ok ?","depth":17},{"id":132,"text":"So we have 50 plus 200 plus almost 300 . \"","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"Analysts say","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"tariffs are not the most effective way","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"of putting pressure on China ,","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"which the US accuses of unfair trade practices and stealing intellectual property from US companies .","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"Syracuse University economics professor Mary Lovely and researcher Yang Liang found","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"87 % of electronics products","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"to be levied by US tariffs","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"came from multinationals and joint ventures rather than Chinese firms .","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"China ' s economy is no longer as dependent on exports .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Domestic consumption now accounts for more than half of the country ' s GDP .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Exports to the US account for only 19 % of all of China ' s exports .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"\" The reciprocal tariffs on US $ 50bn of goods in both directions will have minimal impact in China , \"","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Andy Rothman , an investment strategist at Matthews Asia , wrote in a blog this week .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"China ' s tariffs on major US exports like soybeans , sorghum , and autos , target Republican areas ahead of US midterm elections .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"\" The impact on the US political environment is , however , likely to be far greater , \"","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"One area","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"that will be hurt by US tariffs","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"is China ' s high tech industries , in things like new energy vehicles , robotics and other forms of smart manufacturing ,","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"that form the country ' s \" Made in China 2025 \" industrial plan .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Cheng Dawei , a professor of international trade at Renmin University in Beijing , says","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"these industries are still in their early stages","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"and need inputs from global supply chains .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"\" In the short run , China will be affected badly ...","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"But the tariffs will bring double-lose results .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"China is never the only side","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"to suffer , \"","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"she said .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"\" Imposing high tariffs definitely hurts China badly ,","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"but we will not be beaten down . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":325,"left":164,"right":324,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":164,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":212,"right":323,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":185,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":179,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":165,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":166,"right":177,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":174,"right":176,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":172,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":6,"right":171,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":171,"left":7,"right":170,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":170,"left":169,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":8,"right":168,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":168,"left":9,"right":167,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":173,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":15,"right":175,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{